The storekeeper should have mentioned that about the medicine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Puja Shrestha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR8Jqpz1w7PMn9IJJ8AvX2xuZE1N0X7d_A2gIjDdGQvm1AZqsp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could, I would give negative star. [{"Name":"Bimal Karki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCqbSynlsycPJpRRqNFCP19zOKWG1OHSKQtTafaqYtX87tV-LV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From my experience, Apollo Life Care Pvt. Ltd., Banasthali is a very reliable and well-managed pharmacy. Their long opening hours, friendly staff, and quick service with delivery options make them my trusted choice for healthcare needs. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhBV6nv8HaFe3ve6pO6uFgA0&fid=0x0:0xcea71958b4ba9bf9"],"When":"2025-8-17"},{"Name":"Ram Subedi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxxOlWN10xbbdfKEDyJjVF5pQNLGaV02zvmQPapkPBuPXiwQ-Uug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apollo Life Care is a multi-facility private clinic in the neighborhood, just a few hundred meters from my home. It is run by Hem Raj, a young, energetic, and dynamic individual. The clinic offers various services, including a pharmacy and consultations in internal medicine, gynecology, orthopedics, and ophthalmology. Diagnostic facilities include lab examinations and ultrasounds. The pharmacy provides a wide range of prescription medicines at discounted prices. Additionally, the clinic offers first aid, minor surgery, and management of wounds and minor fractures by competent paramedics. Apollo Life Care has been a great service to the people of Chamati and Banasthali. I frequently visit this clinic for routine checks, including sugar and other biochemistry and pathology examinations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICzupGmaA&fid=0x0:0xcea71958b4ba9bf9"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Sudip Adhikari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHoGunE_bYDdrZ6xn-Frvm8KMec3x6f_rpEWMkjlaFueoTuGCw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best healthcare centre at Kathmandu. It is probably the most economical private healthcare center.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rajiv Tiwari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY0wYf45nG1bJfLQAg6be2nMDIOEcKmx9xSn7E4gWWBKi4DIKu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Apollo life care  and was thoroughly impressed with the level of care and professionalism provided. From the moment I walked in, the staff greeted me warmly and made me feel comfortable. The facility itself was clean, modern, and well-equipped, creating a welcoming atmosphere.

The medical team at there  was exceptional. They listened attentively to my concerns, conducted a thorough examination, and explained everything in a clear and understandable manner. I felt confident in their expertise and knew I was in good hands.

Furthermore, the efficiency of the clinic's operations was noteworthy. Despite the busy schedule, I never felt rushed during my appointment, and the wait times were minimal.

Overall, my experience at there exceeded my expectations. I highly recommend this polyclinic to anyone in need of quality medical care. Thank you to the entire team for their outstanding service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashish Dhakal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV76-XDZhfwjsoDhAZEEjgGDQ3j2sNKvHVxWPicZBEyqr86jmn-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service and quick reports. The staff is very cooperative. Highly recommended for health checkups in Kathmandu!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lekhnath Dhakal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVak0gNSOw_C19zw9GjaRdpO-J6YQDsxQfPOPlZemeThWQiwcDdKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Completely satisfied with overall health facilities🙏🏻🙏🏻","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Tamang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCOReZtE734dX4-oH_UvDxsbW9bF7YU_GnpkZx9Nnl_sWjHJ23=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"i like this pharmacy and i would like to perfer this pharmacy for every one .once you visit you will never get  any dissappointment .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sujindra Maharjan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXySd8JZ1U7OX9GnJ9xxboGqs8V4fUr7lrS192b4pijUtuhFMvI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"though it provide excellent service.do cross check your bill always and ask for the bill. you never know when u are cheated on the bills just like me.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Oleg S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgCTntyfkgRjabGY7TdhOJFM5a6vXhukWr-zOafNdSRy5OxuihRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pharmacy in Kathmandu! We’ve been going there for two years in a row to stock up before trekking in the mountains. The pharmacist is extremely kind and genuinely committed to helping. He suggested all the necessary medicines for trekking. Highly recommended for a hassle-free experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sulav Katwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPSH11agSKHuqRsq6U9ny-HFNoCY0LZIFPYM8SL1egVf0kcWbarw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very disappointing experience. The owner tries to overcharge foreigners and isn’t polite to anyone — just focused on selling at a high price. When we politely asked if there was any discount since we were buying in bulk, he became extremely rude and unprofessional, even speaking disrespectfully to female customers. It’s not about the price, it’s about the attitude. Totally unacceptable behavior — wouldn’t recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5ul0I6LYhYFfWSR6KbygxmrnSE4QbdHiSzIFs1BIK5hKwUH_l6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Come here to get everything you need for a trek. The pharmacist was a very nice man who spoke perfect English. I told him I was going on a 2 week trek and he gave me everything that was on my list before I could ask. He was very honest and didn't try to sell me extra stuff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSAbiGRc2D-1KGKnjdg6Ka9FiW54MV8ZtIE3oBSACY8p8drw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly helpful and very well stocked! I got everything I needed and then the pharmacist suggested a few extra things that I had completely forgotten about but absolutely needed and am very glad I now have. The pharmacist speaks great English and the prices are very reasonable. I absolutely plan to return and am recommending this pharmacy to all other travelers I meet!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tessa Middendorp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmNRXHiBJ0Oiy1fVzjbHN8Oo0CX5f8IJGh8A118nqlQv8SQANL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pharmacist in kathmandu! Very helpfull, and in a few questions I got the right medication.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tinka Huti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-7P6ANVrH3lG9t6Otc6LmrqnG2MdgwDDJ0Ia4JBgpHAUAlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good selection, excellent service! I went to buy few things for trekking - he recommended me all I would need with me. And indeed, ended up needing everything I bought for 9 day trek.

Went back to the same pharmacy after trek! Highly recommended! Thanks again for your kind service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Al_ _ex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgPsIJYkwNIYSLuV2KHbQ0B_qdITPM-cjvRXyiKMrHRvVkWiE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place, I got some trekking relevant medicine. Very nice staff and good location 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kim Sanders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULUwUPDGkmmlQC02cYlayAMPQwPxvaavi9igsFvKFKSV0Npw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend and I had just finished our trek and had arrived back in Kathmandu when she unexpectedly needed pads/tampons. We didn't know where to go but found this place right away - very close to our hostel, Wanderthirst - and found some pads! We were so happy to find some so immediately.

It's a small, grab-and-go type of pharmacy but perfect for any small necessities you may have forgotten for your travels!","Images":null,"When":""}]

It’s shocking that a place like this is still allowed to operate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Random Things","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqzEDmfJ_MxYS51oxuvvtmFIVnnUOmaVpgnQqjbyLsrV6-Iw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a really disappointing and frustrating experience at this pharmacy. I went in to buy a medicine my doctor had recommended via text. Due to a minor typo—he wrote “butadine” instead of “betadine”—one of the female staff read the message, started laughing, and casually said “we don’t have it” without even trying to understand. Instead of clarifying or helping, she just kept giggling, which felt incredibly rude and unprofessional.

Thankfully, another staff member saw the message and immediately understood what I meant. But by then, I was already upset. I was having a rough day, and being mocked like that, especially in a medical setting, was the last thing I needed.

When you wear scrubs, it’s not just a uniform—it comes with a responsibility to treat people with care and respect. There’s nothing funny about someone coming in for medicine. I genuinely hope the management addresses this behavior. The pharmacy side is well-stocked and reliable, known for providing essential medicines at relatively lower prices, making it a solid choice for regular medical needs.

The derma section offers an impressive range of skincare, grooming, and lifestyle products, including many hard-to-find items. However, prices here tend to be on par with or higher than local chemists and online platforms—even after delivery charges. That said, the wide availability often outweighs the price difference for those seeking specific products. Street-side parking adds to the overall convenience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"priyanshu shah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzG8b0mfDgj8ggg0jxyB_ByfpUBAhNWaFqMZa1C1rL2uDY89h-VA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"They have every medicine one needed but they dont provide any discount","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mishraz LotusNepal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWr8SSjDD-VOV6gROVjJuJB1QJvBc9GkhAqq6RedevSGyjau7VX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice place for all kind of medicine ..lack of parking","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"alpa badani Shakya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT7zDP184WqICB-bxqI0twI2D6zls-P4i8qr4RCz4xmsdNEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good service, good staff and sometimes even help on the phone.","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Mangal Bazar
user_reviews: [{"Name":"Raisha Sthapit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6gjwCC7ekO5pdkzBCO0dre1OsF74GLP0iOZGpVQCsj6j2gN1q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mangal Bazar is filled with historical places from temples to museums and fascinating nooks and crannies.\nLocal businesses thrive there as it is a hot destination for tourists. The local people living there are very warm and welcoming and when asked will tell you all about the history of this place. When you visit Mangal Bazar, you will find different restaurants, cafes and even vendors that will serve you hot beverages. It is also the oldest shopping destination where you can also find daily goods.\nThe ambience of Mangal Bazar is totally different which you will not find anywhere else. It is a must visit place when you are in K-town to have fun and spend time with your family and friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgID619mbSA\u0026fid=0x0:0xdc3ef252c2febe01"],"When":"2021-10-14"},{"Name":"Thapa Aashray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4WtnrvrG0XRj3zc-fAZzefjUaIsMjLuABhX4GwrS05DC8h2ab=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I always love this place. Being here gives the best feeling ever. It’s a busy street and I love this place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC2nq-XcQ\u0026fid=0x0:0xdc3ef252c2febe01"],"When":"2022-4-21"},{"Name":"Abhinav Joshi (Nepali Food Traveller)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeI69QSWC-HbAWzu-l_WLY38iUvY_wQLy0tsEO8NwH0Rrjsso-Ag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most wonderful location in Patan city. It has a great historical value as well as religious importance. The area is a great tourist destination but also a great place for spending time for locals. It is one of the best local hangouts and fully packed all day long.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ichchha Ghale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJRHjEPR3iB7qG2MzS_d_OCR3WDc4n8mEamFu-AmOtB8BIv8dW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very chill place to stroll around and hang out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICUira2LQ\u0026fid=0x0:0xdc3ef252c2febe01"],"When":"2019-7-11"},{"Name":"Anish Maharjan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1TrBTa5ieim1gQR5P2jgUfbghMlNZDLztHoxOzI58YyXfM54m=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mangal bazar is a historic city of Lalitpur, Nepal. There are many historical temples of different goddesses. The most important place on this location is Patan Durban Square, which is the palace of the king of Patan(Lalitpur). This place is listed on world heritage sitep. This place is very significant place for the Hindu people of nepal and the world as well. And there are very attractive and ancient historic arts on the temples and other structures and sculptures. Many international tourists visit this place as  a part of their travel.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nilashu Thapa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoWD5zC2KCET71IeFnIeV-fKg4i8sqg9sGUIkM7_NNFPR0STur=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A quite old market with historical importance. This market kids within the vicinity of Patan Durbar Square, one of the enlisted world cultural heritage by UNESCO. You can find almost every day consumables to prayer materials as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Praveen Gola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnJ2EYe7dej2VGU4kHi8WYOK7-kYado0g3RZFSkRzNACYuSIqY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Though crowded but still a beautiful place for shopping and dine.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICE0YOVyQE\u0026fid=0x0:0xdc3ef252c2febe01"],"When":"2017-4-26"},{"Name":"Lumanti Maharjan Chitrakar (Lumu)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcAAVypGzW9_41Lyn7d-41SthLS0dIa0x2RNhY7OTbH58J87CvUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mangalbazar is always lively for shopping, festivals and events. Many temples like Krishna Mandir, Bhairav Mandir, Shiva Mandir, Kartik Naach Stage, Patan Museum, Patan Durbar Square, Nasal chowk, manga hiti (mnagalbazar stone tap) and many more.","Images":null,"When":""}]

This is believed to have been built during medieval period. This is a gate in the medieval period that allowed people to enter and exit at Patan. It does not have magnificent architect but the paintings drawn every year is artistic and replicates art and architect of Nepali culture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIC8iNDaMw&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2020-6-22"},{"Name":"Jenish World","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXya1Vf9_gKQ8t6bg_jV5-9oGKHFOrjqNxbA0Ty2vnb2vOFDlk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is the gateway to the very old Patan valley.  From the looks of 20th century photographs, this gate was redesigned and reopened multiple times. After the devastating earthquake of 1878 A.D., the gate underwent the renovation that gave it its current appearance.    Patan Valley, which is rich in cultural heritage, was ruled by the Lishchavi and Malla lineages in ancient times and is written in temples and inscriptions.  Therefore, this door that enters Patan, now known as Patan door, is also found in the history of the construction of the ancient times.  This door was built during the Malla era, as well as various destructive earthquakes, the architecture of this door has been destroyed and various old photos have shown that this door was built in different styles.  Presently this door is white in color and the door is decorated with various symbols of Ashtamatrika, Ganesha, Kumar, which represent the deities of various Matha temples in Patan.  Therefore, it is an outstanding heritage with a very important history.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICLhu2wCQ&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2024-6-18"},{"Name":"Amit Yadav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmPhmfQRmCZiuMiKT5sFqLEBWcvOPKzilHThmfGv7ywUgShJAx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Patan Dhoka is the entrance gate of the beautiful city Patan. This Dhoka is painted with beautiful pictures during Malla period which reflects the art of Nepali Culture. This gate is one of the most historical gate in Nepal. Don't miss to visit this Patan Dhoka when you are around lalitpur.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDyy7SFdQ&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2021-3-17"},{"Name":"Ashish Amatya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl2PkYYDRQjLUJ_0Wxc8RoMyiWTVIecsPcs44QUKI03nb-CSDRDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ionic place which symbolize the entry point of patan. The gate is hystorically very important landmark in Nepal built more than 100 years ago.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICy4KeAGA&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2021-1-16"},{"Name":"Suman Adhikari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH5bZOC5raZRwhiKevQx7MvPOBfeDCaWMN9TD10FA1i-lg9TFDXg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"No one knows precisely when the Patan Dhoka was first constructed, but it was likely sometime during the Malla period (13th – 18th centuries). It has been refurbished many times over the centuries, including after the infamous 1934 earthquake when it was severely damaged. Most recently, it received a facelift in 2018 when it was repainted to honor the Asta Matrika—eight divine mothers of Hinduism.

The old city of Patan once had more than a half-dozen entry points, but this was the main gate to the municipality, which is also commonly called Lalitpur. The Newari people, the dominant ethnic group in the neighborhood around the gate, originally called the city Yala after King Yalamber who ruled here circa 800 BC. Patan became part of the Gorkha Empire in 1768 when the modern nation of Nepal began, and it is regarded as the oldest city in the Kathmandu Valley.

Before the 2018 refurbishment, the gate was painted with images and messages supporting the Nepal Bhasa Movement (a protest organization that began shortly after the Gorkha annexation), which campaigns to preserve Newari culture and language. In particular, the gate displayed the Nepal Sambat, the lunisolar calendar of the Newari which is still used nationwide in Nepal.

Although the recent murals significantly changed the gate’s previous ornamentation, the design is a traditional Newari paubha painting, a style similar to the better known Tibetan thangka. The Matrika were chosen for their eternal tantric power and as protectors of the Newari people. These mother-goddesses can be depicted as a group of seven, eight, or nine deities depending on the region and holy text being referenced, and the artists of the Patan Dhoka chose eight goddess figures: Brahmani, Vaishnavi, Maheshvari (Rudrani), Indrani, Kaumari, Varahi, Narasimhi, and Chamunda. Flanking the main arch are statues of Ganesh and Kumar, while the tympana of the two smaller arches are adorned with the wrathful image of Cheppu, a mythical Nepali water creature.

According to Lok Chitrakar, the artist who oversaw the mural project, many of the images are not normally seen in public art as they are typically painted in personal spaces as Newari invocations of well-being and prosperity for a household. The gate’s unique style, however, has become a point of unity and civic pride making it an even greater focal point for neighborhood projects and events.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKENW3p6_t86z0Sg&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2025-5-31"},{"Name":"Md Jaid Ahamad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7pStBxSD4VVMlDpabgsY1fBS8o0iMSD-Rr42s7Vr3BqnlyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Every year the gate is painted, the scriptures are in newari languages, and there are beautiful arts on the gate, it is marvelous. One can stop and admire its beauty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICMkKXDjQE&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2019-11-2"},{"Name":"Rumina Shakya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFjcSUZayLLznMSGIFJE__i9L8k9VV9OAJILgi9qX25HJgI4oE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dhoka means entrance gate in Newari language. This is the gateway to Patan. This gate is one of the historical entrance to the old City of Patan.
Recently, it has received a makeover and transformed into a beautiful structure of art.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDE9NCYdw&fid=0x0:0xf3ed1a3f036d8f89"],"When":"2019-1-26"}]

Beyond its administrative duties, the office plays a pivotal role in fostering community engagement and civic participation. Through outreach programs, public forums, and community initiatives, it strives to empower residents and promote a sense of belonging and responsibility towards the municipality.

Excellent service and very humble staffs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Destiny Who","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUN5lJh1fPz9YsUJXbUkV-eborEoAHf_sZKQv9Z7AIRBCYoDsUD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been a loyal customer of this salon since 2021. I have gotten my hair colored, trimmed and styled.

My experience with coloring my hair have been nothing but terrible. They are inexperienced and don’t understand the concept of chemicals in the dye. My scalp was burnt and yet they reapplied the same dye again because it wasn’t “dark enough”. I have never been in so much pain in my life from coloring my hair. This was a big red flag for me .

I decided to never get my hair dyed there again but instead get my hair trimmed and styled. I come there very frequently to get a blow out. The way they’ve styled my hair have been inconsistent. Sometimes it’s beautiful sometimes I question why I still go there? The inconsistency in quality of service is disappointing.

IMPORTANT: Their staff receptionist during evening shifts have been very unprofessional. She lacks friendliness and a smile on the face when talking to customers. This is a service, every business should make sure the customer is comfortable with the service and the way staff treat them. This is one of the main reason why stopped going there. There was also this lady who would always style my hair, but she always had an attitude with me. Never smiled, never said hello, never asked what I wanted. These two ladies have been disappointing in their attitudes towards customers. Their lack of customer service SHOWS. (I usually don’t say anything and I have always tipped the store and been nice to everyone, but now I finally need to speak up)

Final tip to this place. Either train your workers to understand the basics of customer service or fire them respectfully. I hope no one gets to experience what I went through, it’s truly sad because I was there since 2021 and hoped it would change every time. Kapaal salon in Jhamsikhel, please do better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nirdesh Bista","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVyG75zcKe_26HvNNgTPzv9K8MSr5rJzcE0IA_1Up1jtvbXeza=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gave him 100 instructions. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Abhishek Joshi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVefHwtNDrxJc-r0Qd_ZDbtVcs4Z5hyxMKkwLxNsO7Ij4oS4p9y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Having attended and even organized multiple events at The Plaza, I can confidently say it stands out as one of the finest event venues in the city. From the moment you arrive, the experience is defined by thoughtful planning and exceptional execution. One of the most immediate and appreciated features is the ample, well-organized parking space. With clearly marked separate entry and exit points, traffic flow is managed seamlessly, eliminating the congestion and stress so common at large gatherings. This attention to logistical detail sets the tone for the entire event.
The venue itself is both impressive and versatile. The event space is remarkably spacious, featuring three beautifully designed ballrooms that can be easily combined into two or even one grand hall thanks to retractable walls. This flexibility makes it perfect for events of all sizes, from intimate gatherings to large-scale functions. The modern, elegant aesthetic is complemented by superb lighting and decor, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that feels both luxurious and comfortable. Furthermore, the ample outdoor terrace space provides a fantastic alternative for food catering or mingling, ensuring that even when the indoor space is full, guests are never cramped.
A major highlight is the exceptional food catering. The culinary team consistently delivers high-standard, quality food that exceeds expectations in both presentation and taste. Beyond the food, the venue is maintained in immaculate condition. The restrooms are consistently clean and regularly serviced—a small but significant detail that truly enhances the guest experience.
What truly makes The Plaza exceptional, however, is its highly supportive staff and robust security. The team is professional, attentive, and always ready to assist at a moment’s notice, ensuring that every event runs smoothly from start to finish. Their dedication, combined with the venue’s impeccable design and functionality, makes The Plaza a reliable and outstanding choice for any event. I have thoroughly enjoyed every occasion I’ve attended here and cannot recommend it highly enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhA4xdDp_v3AVm8j0iwI26vm&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-8-31"},{"Name":"Techie Rohit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIYryHC2LYDsTaWVoQSmr5nRiv4OzcYxE5vnN8AukQjuX2vZHXzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place for party. Food is good here.
Lovely environment. Good place for kids and adults","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhCjUmsXXnwPoVN0nbGhSU5X&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-12-31"},{"Name":"Kajin Khayamali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHsfspFYfEQUTTCe40rd-QLV3mCO6bCMdv7uEyj3UrELxXjmd3Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently attended the launch party of BIZstyle Magazine, Grandeur Edition, organized by students of Little Angels College of Management, at The Plaza in Jhamsikhel. The venue has recently opened its banquet hall, designed exclusively for events, and it proved to be an excellent fit for our celebration.

From the very beginning, the venue created a strong impression. The location is convenient, and the parking system is well-managed, with separate entry and exit points that help control traffic flow. The banquet hall itself is lavish, spacious, and beautifully designed. With elegant décor and impressive lighting, the ambiance felt aesthetic and picture-perfect—ideal for photography and special occasions. A thoughtful touch was the provision of a VIP room, where guests could securely store their bags and belongings during the event.

However, the food was average at best. Some dishes became cold over time, and the desserts, though visually appealing, were disappointing in taste. Since it was a cocktail dinner, the bartender and liquor arrangements were managed separately by us.
The service from the staffs was good but I didn't like the way snacks food being served on a Napkin paper with just a toothpick, which I felt very unprofessional for such a venue. The buffet dinner was decent but did not meet the same premium standard as the setting.

On the positive side, the staff were polite and attentive, but the food quality and service style need considerable improvement to match the elegance of the venue.

Overall: The Plaza is a luxurious, well-equipped, and impressive banquet venue, perfectly suited for launches, celebrations, and corporate events. With improved food quality and more professional service standards, it has the potential to become one of the leading banquet destinations in Kathmandu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhBEElAx3X3KOiQMyTHZfHU1&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-8-28"},{"Name":"Pradeep Rai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaHtFARBxI6dPtQLSdKbjGBHAwBIHEHV82d6ssBgM16ZGT2t7E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently had the opportunity to attend an office anniversary at this venue, hosted by our office. From the moment I arrived, it was clear that the location had been chosen with careful consideration. The venue is conveniently situated, making it easily accessible for guests coming from different parts of the city. One of the standout features was the ample parking space, which included designated areas and clearly marked separate entry and exit points. This thoughtful planning ensured a smooth flow of traffic, minimizing congestion and allowing guests to arrive and depart without hassle.

The event space itself was remarkably spacious, accommodating a large number of guests comfortably without feeling overcrowded. The interiors were clean and tastefully designed with a modern aesthetic that balanced elegance with functionality. In terms of cleanliness, the venue exceeded expectations. The restrooms, often a neglected aspect of large gatherings, were immaculate and regularly serviced throughout the event, which added to the overall positive impression but as we all know that every coin has its two sides apart from all positive feedback it has some bad impression on me too. The cafeteria area is quite congenerated and no proper seat during having dinner. It is only designed for having snacks but not for dinner or food and this plaza will be best for small events and programs only.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhD1cd1VXe40Bm2Q6QH3H507&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-7-21"},{"Name":"Detective explorer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYFNPQxHiBinYtQagAyx-aD1d5copoGooKddCPbTasIRSGYt4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The place may look fancy from the outside, but the management is really poor. Even basic things are not handled properly. When we asked the guard about the restroom, they had no idea. There’s no one in the parking area to guide you, and the unnecessary automatic gates only waste time instead of making things easier.

The staff are rude, unhelpful, and the services are overpriced. Overall, the experience does not match the image they try to show.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIABIhCcgZgL8P3wib2V2mt-lCIP&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-12-7"},{"Name":"Ram Subedi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxxOlWN10xbbdfKEDyJjVF5pQNLGaV02zvmQPapkPBuPXiwQ-Uug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently had the opportunity to attend a wedding reception at this venue, hosted by a close friend who is also a sitting Member of Parliament. From the moment I arrived, it was clear that the location had been chosen with careful consideration. The venue is conveniently situated, making it easily accessible for guests coming from different parts of the city. One of the standout features was the ample parking space, which included designated areas and clearly marked separate entry and exit points. This thoughtful planning ensured a smooth flow of traffic, minimizing congestion and allowing guests to arrive and depart without hassle.

The event space itself was remarkably spacious, accommodating a large number of guests comfortably without feeling overcrowded. The interiors were clean and tastefully designed with a modern aesthetic that balanced elegance with functionality. The ambiance created by the lighting, decor, and layout contributed to a warm and inviting atmosphere, which is not always easy to find in local event venues. In terms of cleanliness, the venue exceeded expectations. The restrooms, often a neglected aspect of large gatherings, were immaculate and regularly serviced throughout the event, which added to the overall positive impression.

That said, the one area where the venue fell short was the catering. While the kitchen and serving areas were clean and appeared to be well-managed, the quality and presentation of the food did not match the otherwise high standards of the venue. The dishes served were only slightly above average in taste and lacked the creativity and refinement one might expect from an event of this scale. For a reception hosted by a prominent public figure, the culinary experience should have been more memorable. With some attention to improving the food quality and variety, this venue has the potential to become one of the top choices for high-profile events in Nepal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEPTpicCyu-GXLw&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-5-17"},{"Name":"Abhinav Joshi (Nepali Food Traveller)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeI69QSWC-HbAWzu-l_WLY38iUvY_wQLy0tsEO8NwH0Rrjsso-Ag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing 3 ballrooms that can be connected to form a huge 12000sq ft ball room. The price paid is definitely worth the service. The ambience elegant and classy and the terrace on both sides of the ball room are also quite open. The staff extremely attentive as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEN_Rs6aMj4uHNA&fid=0x0:0x4ee7cedb6cef87c7"],"When":"2025-5-10"},{"Name":"Prabin Tiwari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYpYT9sXdCoMdSmKYPAwbUEk8g9uezoyXAh-UZBN8HJKdZRUAc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited the plaza for my cousin’s graduation 🎓 ceremony, and it was a wonderful experience. The event center was spacious, clean, and well organized. The seating arrangement and sound system were good, which made the program enjoyable. Overall, it was a great place for hosting graduation functions and other special events. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""}]

They also allow returns and exchanges if needed. Almost all types of medicines are available, including daily-use medications, supplements, wheelchairs, etc.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"global trade solutions and supplyers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6faFQZOIZmnI2aGdUV1pPcpcG7V59ZC5SYugllxEPIEzgIOKn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Acme is the one of many pharmacy shop who can provide all kinds of medicines of different companies from single door. Discount available here minimum 10% depending on medicines you buy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shaurab Lohani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoQVBT3aoV3MOm6FH8n-fS7opsygIjMfiO8K3k_j7PIA4fvgIc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a pharmacy located close to Teaching hospital in Maharajgunj, Kathmandu. This is not in the busiest road and is on the talim kendra junction. The pharmacy has parking available in the adjacent clinic that they operate as well. You can find almost all sorts of prescribed allopathy medicine in this pharmacy. There are around 2-3 attendants at time so the service is quick. In case you do not find the medicines you are looking for you can simple place and order and it should be available at no time. The only downside is the roadside parking if you need some medicines quickly. Since it is in a vip area, most of the time traffic police prohibits from stopping for even seconds.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICklfPMxgE&fid=0x0:0x3e2340edf76c4d71"],"When":"2018-10-24"},{"Name":"Bibek Someone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJU4wDnHyXt2zajfhQJDMSkv-NhUvHKOuKfzxz8Cb_h7jeHMW8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went there to buy Amip 10 (Amiptriptyline), an antidepressant for a family member and ended up buying Arip 10 used for treating a bipolar disorder!!!! Thank god I double checked once I got back home and then hurried to the pharmacy, with an unapologetic grin, ''You should have known by the price you paid. The difference between the cost of those two drugs  is huge!"

Most people in Nepal just trust the pharmacy and I think very few people double-check. In fact most people do not know how to check if the medicines that they have been handed by the pharmacy is accurate or not. Yes I do know mistakes do happen and to err is human, but when you have taken more than 5 minutes, including a few scroll on the computer screen and when the doctor's handwriting is legible, to make such a mistake for psychotropic medicines is nothing but an utter negligence.

Actually their sheer carelessness warrants a 1 star but I will be a little generous and add more as they are conveniently located and at times provide discounts on medicines, so we're not required to go to pharmacies of the government hospitals to save a few rupees.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgMCIuNmrogE&fid=0x0:0x3e2340edf76c4d71"],"When":"2025-3-30"},{"Name":"Prabin Tiwari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYpYT9sXdCoMdSmKYPAwbUEk8g9uezoyXAh-UZBN8HJKdZRUAc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Acme Pharmacy is an excellent place for all medical needs. The staff is knowledgeable, professional, and genuinely helpful, providing clear guidance on medications and usage. Highly recommended for anyone looking for quality service and availability!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nab Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf-1vz9od03ygBKdiBoI28eE_vLO8YBBshE86vsUiBYwLj2vqTtw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"You can get 10% discount on every purchase","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ankit Aryal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmtf08bOuHYsA8tV9u9qIF70o-RN4rkxC0syYuZJJDLq3cpPCN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Please be careful while buying medicine here.
We were supposed to get T. Flontin Tabs (Antibiotics) for infection but the pharmasist gave us FolVin which is acid based medicine used in treatment of alzheimier. My wife googled it just randomly and was shocked to find this out.

We later went to another Pharmasist who told us the medicine given to us were completely wrong from.prescribed one.

Its not only aboout good doctors. Took time to explain everything to me. Testing revealed little, so I had to go to the hospital for imaging. They called me back and had me come in so that they could explain the results. And they didn't mind speaking English! Won't be your favorite part of your trip, but they'll get you back on the road as soon as possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJo3yjmkLaSUs0fOEhcmZ9kCOF9XeMwSPsYqgW2ShT2TtFhLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was suffering with fevers, nausea, dizziness, severe bouts of stomach and gas pain, couldn't keep food down while in a foreign country for the first time. This clinic got me to see an experienced nurse and Dr within minutes of arriving. Did my vitals and bloods, explained the options and created a treatment plan with me that I was comfortable with. I was prescribed and supplied with medications, the information about the medications including when and how to take them. It was all backed up by my lab results which came within 7 hours. Happy to say im already feeling much better and I couldn't be more grateful to the team at MedEx. Much more than just a pharmacy! Thank you all for helping me I will be able to fly home tomorrow pain free!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derek Bolin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0MQLZl31zDN9Qtf81G0jZY8hVv8fotxMTl5m0Vj_cOkRKWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the very unpleasant experience of having a series of abscesses around my hips and thighs as a result of steroid pain injections in my back. (Steroids weaken the immune system). I had two in the U.S. before leaving on vacation and one in Thailand. I had a fourth in Kathmandu and this was the first clinic where the doctor decided to take a culture to see why antibiotics weren’t working well. Nobody else thought to take a culture. I got the results back on my last day in Kathmandu and found out I was resistant to many of the antibiotics they were giving me. I came back to this clinic and was given the correct antibiotics and the abscesses stopped. The doctors at this place are very professional, clearly well-educated and thorough. The front desk staff were amazing too. Also, the visit took less than 30 minutes so no long waits here. I highly recommend them.\n\n(Sorry about the TMI but it was relevant to the review)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adrián Řezníček","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF1hnLL0VqqwScUW0ipEe78kb3WjgZqdEfxXPW8B4Calth8tZdSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice staff, they helped us. Appreciate the Service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgID98K35lgE&fid=0x0:0x8a7b15cba54f30b"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Learn Everything","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW10pHaeUNtMCMtYgPizY5bmQ1wyIhBhbEtYLvDsJFzI5VyPS2t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional Service and Quality Products!

I recently had the pleasure of visiting Wave Pharmacy for my healthcare needs, and I must say, I was thoroughly impressed. From start to finish, my experience was nothing short of outstanding.
First and foremost, the staff at Wave Pharmacy were incredibly knowledgeable and courteous. They took the time to understand my requirements and offered personalized recommendations tailored to my needs. Their professionalism and expertise truly set them apart.
Moreover, I was blown away by the wide range of high-quality products available here. Whether it was medications, medical supplies, or wellness products, they had everything I needed under one roof. The products were all from reputable brands and of the highest standards.
Furthermore, the store's cleanliness and organization were impeccable, creating a pleasant for customers. It's evident that Pharmacy prioritizes hygiene and customer comfort.

Additionally, I was pleasantly surprised by the efficiency of their service. Despite the busy nature of the store, I didn't have to wait long to receive assistance, and the checkout process was swift and hassle-free.

Overall, my experience at Wave Pharmacy exceeded my expectations in every aspect. I wholeheartedly recommend this store to anyone in need of top-notch healthcare products and exceptional service. Five stars without a doubt!","Images":null,"When":""}]

From the moment you enter the pharmacy, you are welcomed by a warm, friendly, and professional team who genuinely care about the well-being of every customer. The staff are extremely kind, polite, and patient, always ready to listen carefully and provide clear guidance without rushing anyone, even during busy hours.

One of the most impressive aspects of this pharmacy is how helpful and knowledgeable the staff are. They take time to explain medicines, dosage, and precautions in a simple and understandable way, which is especially important for elderly patients and those who may feel anxious about their health. Their respectful attitude makes customers feel comfortable asking questions, and they never hesitate to go the extra mile to ensure proper understanding and safety.

Norvic Pharmacy at Imadol also maintains a clean, organized, and well-managed environment, which adds to the sense of trust and reliability. The availability of medicines, efficient service, and responsible handling of prescriptions reflect their strong commitment to healthcare standards. More than just a place to buy medicine, this pharmacy feels like a supportive healthcare partner for the community.

Overall, Norvic Pharmacy, Imadol Branch deserves high praise for its dedication to public service.
